### ==========================================
### 🔔 NOTIFICATION ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================

### Get My Notifications (must be logged in)
GET http://localhost:6868/api/notification

###

### Mark Single Notification as Read
PUT http://localhost:6868/api/notification/NOTIFICATION_ID_HERE/read

###

### Mark All Notifications as Read
PUT http://localhost:6868/api/notification/read-all

###
